OL,3,C'Parking charges will kill our town' -
OL,4,Cwarn Somerset businesses
OL,6,FBusinesses in Midsomer Norton have
OL,7,Ftold ITV News they fear the
OL,8,Fintroduction of parking charges will
OL,9,F'kill the town'.
OL,11,FBath and North East Somerset Council
OL,12,Fwill introduce new emission-based
OL,13,Fcharges in Midsomer Norton and
OL,14,FRadstock in October, where the car
OL,15,Fparks are currently free.
OL,17,FIt says it is needed to help balance
OL,18,Fthe budget and is part of a wider
OL,19,Freview to improve air quality, reduce
OL,20,Fcongestion and encourage alternative
OL,21,Fways to travel.
