OL,3,C'Parking charges will kill our town' -
OL,4,Cwarn Somerset businesses
OL,6,FBut residents fear their high streets
OL,7,Fwill be badly impacted at a time when
OL,8,Ftrade is already struggling.
OL,10,FButcher Phil Day, from Midsomer
OL,11,FNorton, said: "It's another outgoing.
OL,12,FI worked out based on a 40p hourly
OL,13,Fcharge that's another more than #800 a
OL,14,Fyear just to turn up and come to work.
OL,16,F"We're a small independent business
OL,17,Fstruggling, we've struggled all the
OL,18,Fway through covid. We're just getting
OL,19,Fback on our fee and now we've got
OL,20,Fthis."
