OL,3,C'Parking charges will kill our town' -
OL,4,Cwarn Somerset businesses
OL,6,FKaren Starr who runs Out of Asia said:
OL,7,F"It's going to kill the town. I come
OL,8,Fin from Frome so I don't wish to pay
OL,9,Fto park my car every day. We've been
OL,10,Fhere 31 years, and we do okay, but
OL,11,Fit's nothing like it was before that
OL,12,Fpandemic."
OL,14,FIndependent councillor Shaun Hughes
OL,15,Fargues that the decision to introduce
OL,16,Ffees has not been thought through, as
OL,17,Fthere is no issue with air quality and
OL,18,Fhe claims the amount of money the
OL,19,Fscheme will generate is tiny.
