OL,3,C'Parking charges will kill our town' -
OL,4,Cwarn Somerset businesses
OL,6,FCllr Shaun Hughes said: "These
OL,7,Fdecisions are being made by Bath
OL,8,Fcouncillors who have no understanding
OL,9,Fof our fragile local economy.
OL,11,F"They've done no parking surveys or
OL,12,Fimpact assessments. They have no
OL,13,Fcomprehension of what damage it will
OL,14,Fdo to our businesses and our town."
OL,16,FA public consultation is due to take
OL,17,Fplace in May, with the emission-based
OL,18,Fcharges due to be introduced in
OL,19,FOctober.
