OL,3,C'Parking charges will kill our town' -
OL,4,Cwarn Somerset businesses
OL,6,FCouncillor Manda Rigby, cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor Transport, said: "Our review of
OL,8,Fparking charges across Bath and North
OL,9,FEast Somerset was agreed last month as
OL,10,Fpart of setting the council's budget
OL,11,Ffor the coming financial year. Our aim
OL,12,Fis to improve air quality, reduce
OL,13,Fcongestion and encourage other ways to
OL,14,Ftravel.
