OL,3,C'Parking charges will kill our town' -
OL,4,Cwarn Somerset businesses
OL,6,F"Introducing charging in Midsomer
OL,7,FNorton and Radstock would make it
OL,8,Feasier for shoppers to find parking by
OL,9,Fencouraging turnover of spaces, and
OL,10,Fthe additional revenue would support
OL,11,Fregeneration schemes designed to
OL,12,Fincrease footfall and support local
OL,13,Ftrade.
OL,15,F"We will be consulting with residents
OL,16,Fon the wider roll out of proposed
OL,17,Femission-based charges across Bath and
OL,18,FNorth East Somerset later this year."
